title: The Sphere
description: Bullied outcast Rudo finds respite in repurposing trash, until a terrible tragedy changes his life forever.

title: The Inhabited
description: Cast into the Pit, Rudo is saved by the mysterious Enjin who may not have his best interests at heart.

title: The Ground
description: Enjin teaches Rudo about life on the Ground, but an encounter with a churlish stranger may cut his time short.

title: Cleaner HQ
description: After being introduced to Cleaner HQ, Rudo follows Riyo on a job to learn the business.

title: Raiders
description: The Cleaners go on a job to save another Sphereite who survived the fall. Rudo tags along to learn more.

title: One Good Strike!!
description: With the job having gone terribly wrong, Rudo finds himself face to face with a merciless Raider named Jabber.

title: A Score to Settle
description: Jabber employs a new strategy to get through Rudo's defenses, and another ally joins the fray.

title: Moving Forward
description: Rudo deals with the emotional aftermath of the Jabber fight and gets a new lead about returning to the Sphere.

title: The City of Graffiti
description: To get a "spell" for their next mission, the Cleaners head to Canvas Town, where they make a tragic discovery.

title: Penta: The Desert No Man's Land
description: With their gear-up complete, the crew heads into the No Man's Land, Penta, to get clues about the Sphere.

title: Amo's Hospitality
description: A mysterious woman living in the No Man's Land challenges the crew from an unexpected angle.

title: Something Like a Curse
description: Tamsy and Zanka fight to save their captive allies. In the aftermath, Rudo has an unexpected reaction.
